    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was-- at the beginning, first, one, two days, there was disorganize.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe we went to-- we take bathtub, shower.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I believe there was kind of separation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As-- as-- as far as I remember, separation of Polish, Polish Jewish and Polish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning, they [INAUDIBLE] women, only Polish, Polish people.",
